name: Style Sylva Magic
description:
This is a Textual Inversion trained on one image with DreamArtist, my second publicly released inversion. :)

Some images utilized low weights of this fantastic Torino Aqua Style LoRA

Style Sylva Magic gives everything a fairytale-like feel with a lot of soft lighting, flowers, nature, etc. I hope those that download are able to use it to assist in creating beautiful art. :)
